4 SYNOPSIS:
5 This bill would authorize public institutions of
6 higher education to accept Classic Learning Test (CLT)
7 scores to the same extent as American College Test
8 (ACT) and Scholastic Aptitude Test (SAT) scores for
9 demonstrating college readiness and satisfying
10 admissions criteria.
11
12
13 A BILL
14 TO BE ENTITLED
15 AN ACT
16
17 Relating to public institutions of higher education; to
18 authorize the institutions to accept the Classic Learning Test
19 (CLT) to the same extent the institution accepts the American
20 College Test (ACT) and the Scholastic Aptitude Test (SAT) for
21 demonstrating college readiness and satisfying admissions
22 criteria.
23 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
24 Section 1. A state-supported public institution of
25 higher education may accept the Classic Learning Test (CLT) to
26 the same extent the institution accepts the American College
27 Test (ACT) and the Scholastic Aptitude Test (SAT) for
28 demonstrating college readiness and satisfying admissions
